---
title: OuzBot twitter bot
updated: 2019-10-13 23:37
---

OuzBot is a twitter bot to analyze the quality of my followers/friends. It lists them with their public details.
In details, it is a flask web app using Tweepy (Twitter API wrapper for python) deployed on heroku PaaS.

Code source available <https://github.com/Sim4n6/OuzBot>
